At Meow Wolf Denver, was created by @volarduran and David Ocelotl Garcia. It’s an exploration and physical manifestation of energy, sculpture, color and light using a technique David developed called Abstract Imaginism.

Opening Fall 2021

🎥: @valentinovalentin

🎵: @davidlast

node.text:
@shrineon is a brilliant artist and activist who's incorporating his iconic trash art motifs in the form of a mural for @omegamartusa. His work has transcended into a healing method, which is so crucial nowadays. Working with him has been an absolute dream and we can't wait to see his finished mural for Omega Mart.

Directed, Written and Edited by @jilannspitzmiller 
Produced by Isabel Zermani (@magicisrealism)
Cinematography by Morgan Capps, @alupovich and Jilann Spitzmiller
Additional Cinematography courtesy of @thegreatoven by Archie Thomas
@archiethomasdotcom and James Gomez Thompson @j_gomez_thompson
Music: “Below the Sun” by Skygaze

Special thanks to James Thompson & Joe Adamsdale of Great Oven

📸: @kennedycottrell
